               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra, name of the protagonist; incipit of Text I (2 red lines: 1 red line alternating with 1 black line) and of some of its sections (e.g. fols. 3vb, 35rb); word sälam "salutation" and its abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
The name of the original donor, mentioned in the supplication formulas, has been crudely erased and replaced with that of Gäbrä Mädḫǝn, written in deep magenta (e.g., fols. 8ra, 13rb, 18va, 35rb).</rubric>
